testing:
`cargo test --workspace -- --test-threads=1`

migration:
`cargo run --bin migrate`

running:
`cargo run --bin hastebin`

========================================
AI Integration (Conversational Use)
========================================

Purpose: Enable AI assistants to interact with pastes users share in conversations

Endpoints:
- GET /openapi.json - OpenAPI 3.1.0 spec
- GET /.well-known/ai-plugin.json - AI plugin manifest
- GET /ai-instructions - Consolidated guide (serves docs/ai/README.md)

Documentation:
- docs/ai/README.md - Complete integration guide
- docs/ai/example.py - Python reference implementation

Key Concept: URLs use hex IDs (e.g., /abc123), API uses decimal
  User shares:  https://hastebin.ianhon.com/abc123
  AI extracts:  "abc123"
  AI converts:  int("abc123", 16) = 11259375
  AI fetches:   GET /paste/fetch/11259375

Common AI workflows:
1. User shares URL → AI fetches & analyzes code
2. User asks for improvements → AI creates fork
3. User requests review → AI adds comments
4. User needs code → AI creates paste & shares URL